      <title>随着流媒体竞争的加剧，标准普尔将派拉蒙全球置于负面观察名单</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/business/media-telecom/sp-puts-paramount-global-negative-watch-streaming-competition-grows-2024-02-23/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[评级机构标准普尔周五将派拉蒙全球公司的信用评级置于负面观察名单，理由是由于有线电视业务持续下滑和流媒体竞争，该媒体集团运营现金流量较低。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/business/media-telecom/sp-puts-paramount-global-negative-watch-streaming-competition-grows-2024-02-23/</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 23 Feb 2024 17:51:37 GMT</pubDate>
